    "causal_summary": "SpecKit Reimagined synthesizes findings from 25 parallel agent analyses of 8 pre-analysis documents examining dotmd, seu-claude, drift, and system-speckit architectures. This specification defines 15 P0 blockers (10 original + 5 embedding resilience), 18 P1 requirements, and establishes a unified 6-7 week implementation roadmap to transform SpecKit into a best-in-class memory system with hybrid search, causal graphs, embedding resilience, and self-improvement capabilities.",
